Yes, please.

00:25:15.414 --> 00:25:15.848 align:middle line:90%
>>BRADEN: All right.

00:25:15.848 --> 00:25:17.783 align:middle line:84%
I want to talk about
civilization and, then,

00:25:17.783 --> 00:25:20.119 align:middle line:84%
the role of competition
in civilization.

00:25:20.119 --> 00:25:21.820 align:middle line:84%
When I was in school,
you were in school,

00:25:21.820 --> 00:25:27.059 align:middle line:84%
our young people in school
today are being shown a graph,

00:25:27.059 --> 00:25:29.428 align:middle line:84%
a shot very similar to what
you're seeing on the screen

00:25:29.428 --> 00:25:29.928 align:middle line:90%
