underneath earth
under-- there's--

00:27:20.572 --> 00:27:22.074 align:middle line:84%
>>BRADEN: --layers upon
layers upon layers.

00:27:22.074 --> 00:27:22.374 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Layers and layers.

00:27:22.374 --> 00:27:22.941 align:middle line:90%
11,000 years--

00:27:22.941 --> 00:27:24.810 align:middle line:84%
>>BRADEN: But we haven't
gotten to that part.

00:27:24.810 --> 00:27:25.544 align:middle line:90%
You're giving it away.

00:27:25.544 --> 00:27:26.345 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Oh my god.

00:27:26.345 --> 00:27:27.779 align:middle line:84%
>>BRADEN: So this
site right here,

00:27:27.779 --> 00:27:31.116 align:middle line:84%
this site was intentionally
buried 8,000 years ago

00:27:31.116 --> 00:27:33.085 align:middle line:84%
