00:27:39.758 --> 00:27:40.692 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That's amazing.

00:27:40.692 --> 00:27:42.461 align:middle line:84%
>>BRADEN: 8,000 years
ago, but it's older.

00:27:42.461 --> 00:27:44.463 align:middle line:84%
Right now, the
site is being dated

00:27:44.463 --> 00:27:48.400 align:middle line:84%
between 11,300 and
11,500 years ago.

00:27:48.400 --> 00:27:51.803 align:middle line:84%
Twice as old as what we're
being told that civilization

00:27:51.803 --> 00:27:53.105 align:middle line:90%
