has to approve its
own curricula for what

00:28:29.608 --> 00:28:31.176 align:middle line:90%
is taught in the schools.

00:28:31.176 --> 00:28:32.811 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: But if we're
saying-- if you're

00:28:32.811 --> 00:28:35.447 align:middle line:84%
