00:29:31.303 --> 00:29:32.037 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Ah, I see.

00:29:32.037 --> 00:29:32.904 align:middle line:84%
>>BRADEN: Here's why
that's important.

00:29:32.904 --> 00:29:33.205 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yeah.

00:29:33.205 --> 00:29:35.073 align:middle line:84%
>>BRADEN: It means they
