00:29:41.647 --> 00:29:42.881 align:middle line:90%
them get through the changes.

00:29:42.881 --> 00:29:45.517 align:middle line:84%
And it's all based in
this idea of cooperation

00:29:45.517 --> 00:29:46.318 align:middle line:90%
versus competition.

00:29:46.318 --> 00:29:47.119 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That is the main point.

00:29:47.119 --> 00:29:48.887 align:middle line:84%
>>BRADEN: The last piece of
this, it's so fascinating.

00:29:48.887 --> 00:29:49.655 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK, wow.

00:29:49.655 --> 00:29:54.660 align:middle line:84%
>>BRADEN: Archaeologists have
found that large scale war does

00:29:54.660 --> 00:29:59.398 align:middle line:84%
