00:36:51.643 --> 00:36:53.111 align:middle line:90%
One satellite's blue.

00:36:53.111 --> 00:36:54.012 align:middle line:90%
There's a big spike.

00:36:54.012 --> 00:36:57.248 align:middle line:84%
That spike is
September 11, 2001.

00:36:57.248 --> 00:37:00.218 align:middle line:84%
This is the spike that gave
the scientists the heads up.

00:37:00.218 --> 00:37:03.588 align:middle line:84%
It begins at 9:00 AM
Eastern Standard Time,

00:37:03.588 --> 00:37:06.624 align:middle line:84%
15 minutes after the first
plane hit the first tower.

00:37:06.624 --> 00:37:10.762 align:middle line:84%
Scientists believe it took
about 15 minutes for the images

00:37:10.762 --> 00:37:12.630 align:middle line:84%
