emotion, heart-based emotion

00:37:19.971 --> 00:37:21.606 align:middle line:84%
in response to what
people were seeing.

00:37:21.606 --> 00:37:22.774 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That was measurable?

00:37:22.774 --> 00:37:23.475 align:middle line:90%
>>BRADEN: That was measurable.

00:37:23.475 --> 00:37:24.976 align:middle line:84%
This gave scientists
the heads up.

00:37:24.976 --> 00:37:28.113 align:middle line:84%
This gives new meaning
to the Gaia theory

00:37:28.113 --> 00:37:31.916 align:middle line:84%
