to the fields of the Earth.

00:37:31.916 --> 00:37:34.119 align:middle line:84%
This gave scientists the
heads up that, my god,

00:37:34.119 --> 00:37:37.388 align:middle line:84%
we have the ability to
influence the very field

00:37:37.388 --> 00:37:39.424 align:middle line:84%
of the Earth that
connects and sustains

00:37:39.424 --> 00:37:41.359 align:middle line:90%
all life on this planet.

00:37:41.359 --> 00:37:44.295 align:middle line:84%
And we can do it through
heart-based emotion.

00:37:44.295 --> 00:37:47.165 align:middle line:84%
Now, this is in
response to a tragedy.

00:37:47.165 --> 00:37:49.000 align:middle line:84%
The question is, can
it happen because we

00:37:49.000 --> 00:37:51.069 align:middle line:90%
choose to create the experience?

00:37:51.069 --> 00:37:51.402 align:middle line:90%
And that's where we're going.

00:37:51.402 --> 00:37:52.704 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: And how is it measured?

00:37:52.704 --> 00:37:54.439 align:middle line:84%
Well, let's talk about
this a little bit.

00:37:54.439 --> 00:37:56.107 align:middle line:84%
>>BRADEN: Well,
what scientists now

00:37:56.107 --> 00:37:57.909 align:middle line:84%
