00:38:15.226 --> 00:38:15.727 align:middle line:90%
actually.

00:38:15.727 --> 00:38:17.295 align:middle line:90%
It's a very, very low frequency.

00:38:17.295 --> 00:38:18.363 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Huh.

00:38:18.363 --> 00:38:20.832 align:middle line:10%
>>BRADEN: When we feel
the feeling in our heart

00:38:20.832 --> 00:38:23.034 align:middle line:10%
that creates this
optimum frequency,

00:38:23.034 --> 00:38:24.702 align:middle line:10%
we are in high coherence.

00:38:24.702 --> 00:38:27.005 align:middle line:84%
This is where we couple with
the fields of the Earth.

